  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.10">
<l>kaṭivār tīya viṉaikaḷ</l>
<l>noṭiyā rumaḷa vaikkaṇ</l>
<l>koṭiyā vaṭupuḷ ḷuyartta</l>
<l>vaṭivār mātava ṉārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will expell evil karmas</l>
<l>with a snap of [his] finger,</l>
<l>beautiful Mādava</l>
<l>who raise the killing bird as [his] banner.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
